OL,3,CHottest year on record: 2024 was first
OL,4,Cyear to break 1.5C warming threshold
OL,6,FClimate experts said a single year
OL,7,Fwith average temperatures of 1.5C
OL,8,Fabove pre-industrial levels did not
OL,9,Fmean the world had reached that level
OL,10,Fof global warming, though they issued
OL,11,Fwarnings about how close it now was.
OL,13,FBut the record heat should be a
OL,14,F"reality check" with a year of extreme
OL,15,Fweather events showing how dangerous
OL,16,Flife with 1.5C of warming was, one
OL,17,Fexpert said.
