OL,3,CHottest year on record: 2024 was first
OL,4,Cyear to break 1.5C warming threshold
OL,6,FIt was also the 11th year in
OL,7,Fsuccession in the data series that has
OL,8,Fequalled or exceeded 1C above pre-
OL,9,Findustrial levels.
OL,11,FColin Morice of the Met Office said:
OL,12,F"A single year exceeding 1.5C above
OL,13,Fpre-industrial does not mean a breach
OL,14,Fof the Paris Agreement 1.5C guard rail
OL,15,F` that would require a temperature of
OL,16,Fat least 1.5C on average over a longer
OL,17,Fperiod.
