OL,4,Cyear to break 1.5C warming threshold
OL,6,FThe analysis also highlights that
OL,7,Fglobally, each of the past 10 years
OL,8,Fwere one of the warmest 10 years on
OL,9,Frecord.
OL,11,FSamantha Burgess, from the European
OL,12,FCentre for Medium-Range Weather
OL,13,FForecasts (ECMWF) which runs C3S,
OL,14,Fsaid: "We are now teetering on the
OL,15,Fedge of passing the 1.5C level defined
OL,16,Fin the Paris Agreement and the average
OL,17,Fof the last two years is already above
OL,18,Fthis level.
