OL,6,F"These high global temperatures,
OL,7,Fcoupled with record global atmospheric
OL,8,Fwater vapour levels in 2024, meant
OL,9,Funprecedented heatwaves and heavy
OL,10,Frainfall events, causing misery for
OL,11,Fmillions of people."
OL,13,FProfessor Rowan Sutton, director of
OL,14,Fthe Met Office Hadley Centre, said:
OL,15,F"By itself, 1.5C does not represent a
OL,16,Fcliff edge in terms of climate impacts.
