OL,3,CHottest year on record: 2024 was first
OL,4,Cyear to break 1.5C warming threshold
OL,6,F"But every fraction of a degree rise
OL,7,Fin global temperature increases the
OL,8,Ffrequency and severity of extreme
OL,9,Fweather events, commits the world to
OL,10,Fgreater rises in sea level and
OL,11,Fincreases the risk of crossing
OL,12,Fpotential planet-altering tipping
OL,13,Fpoints such as breakdown of the Amazon
OL,14,Frainforest biome or ice sheet collapse
OL,15,Fin Greenland or the Antarctic.
OL,17,F"This notable landmark further
OL,18,Fhighlights the urgency of efforts to
OL,19,Fminimise future warming."
