OL,6,FIn response to the announcement, Dr
OL,7,FFriederike Otto, senior lecturer at
OL,8,Fthe Centre for Environmental Policy,
OL,9,FImperial College London, said: "This
OL,10,Frecord needs to be a reality check.
OL,12,F"The climate is heating to levels
OL,13,Fwe've spent years trying to avoid
OL,14,Fbecause countries are still burning
OL,15,Fhuge amounts of oil, gas and coal. A
OL,16,Fyear of extreme weather showed just
OL,17,Fhow dangerous life is at 1.5C.
